# Scratch working pulls at THIS dir's root — regenerable, and profile.md holds
# personal data. Leading "/" anchors each pattern here so it can't reach into data/
# (the durable version history under data/ IS committed).
/profile.md
/scan-jobs.json
/outreach-messages.json
/baseline-*.md
/style-matrix-*.md
/work-example-audit.json
/work-examples.json
/evidence-manifest.json
/*.next
/data/**/*.next
